    "Title": "~mission(ReputationRank) Rank - Direct ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Cargo Haul",
    "Description": "Hiya, \n\nLooking for a hauler willing to make a run to Ruin Station. Know hauls to Pyro can give some people pause, but this is one we do regularly to help supply the station. I\u2019ve also confirmed that everything on the cargo manifest is above board. \n\nIf you\u2019re interested, the cargo is ready for pick up at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>.  Make sure you bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> and a ship that can hold <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4> otherwise it might be a little rough.\n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nElla Tieno \nJr. Logistics Coordinator \nCovalex Shipping   \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.' \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
